<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.572512>
    dc:description "FIGURE 38. Metaventrite of Irenimus crinitus, left lateral view, showing pappolepida (white dart). Scale bar = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/572512/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.572509>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29 – 34. Left metatibia, anterior view. 29, Irenimus minimus; 30, Irenimus parilis; 31, Irenimus parilis, apical view; 32, Irenimus duplex; 33, Irenimus duplex, apical view; 34, Chalepistes compressus. Abbreviations: cl – corbel; sc—setal comb; ve—ventral emargination. Drawings not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/572509/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.572513>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39 – 40. Pronotum, dorsal view with head to top of image. 39, Irenimus duplex; 40, Irenimus thoracicus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/572513/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

